♪And I see you again♪

243
00:15:05,310 --> 00:15:07,030
♪You left♪

244
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,870
♪Broke my heart♪

245
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:12,920
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

246
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:15,750
♪Even your name♪

247
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:20,230
♪Is a forbidden word♪

248
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:24,330
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

249
00:15:24,330 --> 00:15:28,580
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

250
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:32,030
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

251
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:35,980
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

252
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:39,760
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

253
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:43,640
♪Only to call your name again♪

254
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:47,690
♪For it's the only thing♪

255
00:15:47,970 --> 00:15:51,700
♪I'll never forget♪

256
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:55,220
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

257
00:15:55,220 --> 00:15:59,530
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

258
