♪For it once shone upon your face♪

259
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:07,570
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

260
00:16:07,690 --> 00:16:10,750
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

261
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:14,690
♪Only to call your name again♪

262
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:18,400
♪For it's the only thing♪

263
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:22,700
♪I'll never forget♪

264
00:16:26,570 --> 00:16:29,940
♪Till the day that I die♪
